<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
    xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
    xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
    xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
    metal:use-macro="base">
    <tal:block metal:fill-slot="content">
    <div class="row">
	    <div class="pre_2 col_4">
            <div>
                <div id="concept_front">
                    <h1><img src="${images_static_url}/concept_front.png" alt="Concept"/></h1>
                    <p><img src="${images_static_url}/concept_front_image.png" alt="hop image"/></p>
                </div>
                <p i18n:translate="">Fluid Nexus is an application for Android phones and desktop computers enabling exchange of messages without the need for centralized mobile networks.  Messages are transferred by short-range networking technologies like bluetooth and through the movement of people from one location to another.  <a href="/infos/concept">Read More</a>; <a href="/infos/faq">Read the FAQs</a></p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div id="nexus_front">
                    <h1><img src="${images_static_url}/nexus_front.png" alt="Nexus"/></h1>
                </div>
                <p i18n:translate="">The Nexus is the location for public messages uploaded by users of the Fluid Nexus software.  The stream provides a real-time view of text, images, audio, and video that Fluid Nexus users think should be seen by the general public.  <a href="/nexus">View the Nexus</a></p>
            </div>
	    </div>
        <div class="col_4 last">
            <div>
                <div id="download_front">
                    <h1><img src="${images_static_url}/download_front.png" alt="Download"/></h1>
                    <p><img src="${images_static_url}/download_front_image.png" alt="app screenshots"/></p>
                </div>
                <p i18n:translate="">Fluid Nexus is available for Android phones and computers running Windows or Linux.  <a href="/download">More info</a></p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div id="connect_front">
                    <h1><img src="${images_static_url}/connect_front.png" alt="Connect"/></h1>
                </div>
                <h2 i18n:translate=""><img src="${images_static_url}/identica.png" alt="identi.ca"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://identi.ca/fluidnexus">identi.ca</a></h2>
                <h2 i18n:translate=""><img src="${images_static_url}/twitter.png" alt="twitter"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://twitter.com/FluidNexus">twitter</a></h2>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div id="donate">
                    <h1>Donate</h1>
                    <p>You can donate to our bitcoin address: 18GD6vMjmXthGhDNDhNMEoEthoGkUXkQR3.  Even a fraction of a coin helps us know that our work is appreciated.  Thanks!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </tal:block>
</html>
